Modifications in this fork (Qwen3-TTS-JP-mac):
- macOS Apple Silicon (MPS) device support with automatic detection
- Japanese GUI localization for Gradio demo
- Whisper automatic transcription integration (optional)
- FlashAttention-2 replaced with SDPA for macOS compatibility
- Device/dtype/attention auto-detection utilities (qwen_tts/utils/device.py)
- devbox + uv development environment setup
- macOS-focused setup script and documentation
